				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ h = \frac{1}{2}n\lambda = \frac{1}{2}n\frac{c}{f},\;n = 1,2,3 $$\end{document}

